OL,3,CHammer-wielding masked men terrorise
OL,4,Cbeauty salon
OL,6,FThe owner of a beauty salon in
OL,7,FNottinghamshire has been left
OL,8,F'heartbroken' after her business was
OL,9,Ftwice attacked by vandals over a
OL,10,Fperiod of just three weeks.
OL,12,FThe Lash Lounge in Beeston was first
OL,13,Fhit on 13 November when bricks were
OL,14,Fthrown at its windows.
OL,16,FOwner Sarah Clay thought it was a
OL,17,Frandom incident until a second attack
OL,18,Fthis week. CCTV showed two masked and
OL,19,Fhooded individuals attacking the salon
OL,20,Fwith what appeared to be hammers.
