OL,4,Cbeauty salon
OL,6,FSarah says she has no idea why her
OL,7,Fbusiness is being targeted.
OL,9,FSpeaking to ITV News Central, Sarah
OL,10,Fsaid: "It's been horrendous. We've
OL,11,Fbeen extremely stressed. We have been
OL,12,Ffearful. We have been nothing short of
OL,13,Fheartbroken."
OL,15,FShe said she's now resorted to locking
OL,16,Fherself and her customers in the salon
OL,17,Fbecause she feels so vulnerable.
OL,19,FShe added: "The financial implications
OL,20,Fthat it's having on us could mean that
OL,21,Fwe're no more.
