OL,6,F"I have nine girls who rent spaces
OL,7,Fhere (so it's) not just me that's
OL,8,Fgoing to be out of work, it would be
OL,9,Fnine people."
OL,11,FNottinghamshire Police is
OL,12,Finvestigating the incidents with
OL,13,Fofficers still attempting to trace the
OL,14,Fsuspects.
OL,16,FA spokesperson for the force said:
OL,17,F"These incidents have caused a great
OL,18,Fdeal of distress to the salon owner
OL,19,Fand we are doing everything we can to
OL,20,Ffind those responsible.
