OL,6,F"We are in the process of analysing
OL,7,Favailable CCTV footage to establish
OL,8,Fexactly what happened and who could
OL,9,Fhave been responsible.
OL,11,F"At this stage, we're working on the
OL,12,Fbasis that these incidents could be
OL,13,Flinked."
OL,15,FAnyone with information that could
OL,16,Fassist the investigation is asked to
OL,17,Fcall 101.
